title: Week 3 NFL Recap (Football 09/24)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down every single game from Week 3 of the 2018 NFL season. Are the 49ers sunk with Jimmy Garoppolo's injury? Are the Rams the best team in football? Would Sean trade Mitchell Trubisky for Ryan Tannehill? Is the Patriots dynasty dead? All these questions answered, plus analysis on every single game from the Week 3 slate, all served up with a side of mirth.
